window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Contains books one and two of the Perfect Stranger series. </b></p> <p><i>The Perfect Stranger</i>, book one</p> <p>Who is he? What does he want? He takes a step closer to me, and I realize that I know him.</p> <p>I haven’t seen him in years, but I’ve never stopped thinking about him. He is dark, rich, and powerful, and he has a secret. Anger rushes through me. Who does he think he is coming here? But when I open my mouth to yell at him, our lips touch, and I can’t pull away....</p> <p><i>The Perfect Cover</i>, book two</p> <p>He doesn’t belong here. He is tall, gorgeous, and handsome and with a dark secret. Everyone in the country is looking for him, and he’s hiding in my home. He’s my obsession, and I’m his addiction.</p> <p>There’s a knock on my door. Time is running out. I have to make a choice. They are here....</p>"; 
